<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 01:10:54 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>台湾总统将访问太平洋岛国盟友</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-president-visit-pacific-island-nation-allies-2024-11-22/</link><description>台湾总统府周五表示，总统赖清德将访问台湾的太平洋岛国盟友，这可能意味着他还将在​​美国领土上进行敏感的过境停留，此举可能会激怒北京。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 00:11:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-president-visit-pacific-island-nation-allies-2024-11-22/</guid></item><item><title>习近平访问摩洛哥并会见王储</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-visits-morocco-meets-with-crown-prince-says-state-media-2024-11-22/</link><description>据国家通讯社MAP报道，中国国家主席习近平周四对摩洛哥进行了短暂访问。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 00:00:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-visits-morocco-meets-with-crown-prince-says-state-media-2024-11-22/</guid></item><item><title>随着贸易紧张局势加剧，中国企业寻求美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/corporate-china-seeks-dollars-trade-tensions-rise-2024-11-21/</link><description>由于贸易紧张局势可能会扰乱外汇汇率，中国企业正在储备更多美元，以人民币定价合同，并开放进口额度，以减轻货币风险。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 23:06:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/corporate-china-seeks-dollars-trade-tensions-rise-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：韧性是游戏的名称，关注日本 CPI</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-11-21/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 21:52:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>国际原子能机构理事会通过伊朗决议，西方推动德黑兰进行谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/un-nuclear-watchdogs-35-nation-board-passes-resolution-against-iran-2024-11-21/</link><description>目的是迫使伊朗就对其核活动的新限制进行谈判。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 21:01:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/un-nuclear-watchdogs-35-nation-board-passes-resolution-against-iran-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>政府称埃克森集团退出与圭亚那浅水石油区块的谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/exxon-mobil-pulls-out-talks-with-guyana-over-shallow-water-oil-block-gov-says-2024-11-21/</link><description>圭亚那副总统周四表示，美国石油巨头埃克森美孚及其合作伙伴已退出与圭亚那政府就勘探和开发浅水石油区块条款进行的谈判。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 20:28:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/exxon-mobil-pulls-out-talks-with-guyana-over-shallow-water-oil-block-gov-says-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>因安全担忧引发 FCC 提议对中国视频门铃制造商处以罚款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/fcc-proposes-fine-chinese-video-doorbell-manufacturer-after-security-concerns-2024-11-21/</link><description>美国联邦通信委员会周四提议对中国视频门铃制造商 Eken 处以近 735,000 美元的罚款，原因是其提供虚假信息并引发安全担忧。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 16:51:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/fcc-proposes-fine-chinese-video-doorbell-manufacturer-after-security-concerns-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国指责美国对台政策导致防务领导人未会面</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-blames-us-policy-taiwan-defence-leaders-not-meeting-2024-11-21/</link><description>中国国防部指责美国对台湾的立场，导致中国国防部长本周在老挝举行的一次会议上没有与美国国防部长会面。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 14:22:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-blames-us-policy-taiwan-defence-leaders-not-meeting-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国声称“消灭”了缅甸北部的大型电信诈骗中心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-claims-wipe-out-large-telecom-fraud-centres-northern-myanmar-2024-11-21/</link><description>中国官方媒体周四报道称，中国和缅甸执法机构已“消灭”了在缅甸北部运营的所有大型电信诈骗中心，周末的一次行动逮捕了 700 多人。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 13:06:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-claims-wipe-out-large-telecom-fraud-centres-northern-myanmar-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>香港民主活动人士黎智英否认在审判中煽动对中国的仇恨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-democracy-activist-jimmy-lai-denies-inciting-hatred-towards-china-2024-11-21/</link><description>民主活动人士黎智英周四在具有里程碑意义的国家安全审判中作证的第二天表示，他反对暴力，并没有通过呼吁抗议来捍卫基本权利来煽动对中国和香港当局的仇恨。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 12:24:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-democracy-activist-jimmy-lai-denies-inciting-hatred-towards-china-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国信托之星融资10亿美元，收购麦当劳中国股份</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-trustar-raises-1-bln-vehicle-that-holds-mcdonalds-china-stake-sources-say-2024-11-21/</link><description>两位知情人士称，Trusstar Capital 已为一只持续基金筹集了 10 亿美元，该基金将持有这家中国私募股权公司在麦当劳公司中国大陆和香港业务中的控股权。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 11:52:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-trustar-raises-1-bln-vehicle-that-holds-mcdonalds-china-stake-sources-say-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：英伟达预计将实现三位数增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-11-21/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 11:26:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>在对特朗普关税的担忧之际，中国宣布促进贸易的政策措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-announces-policy-measures-boost-trade-amid-worries-over-trump-tariffs-2024-11-21/</link><description>中国商务部周四宣布了一系列旨在促进中国对外贸易的政策措施，包括承诺加强对企业的融资支持和扩大农产品出口。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 10:18:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-announces-policy-measures-boost-trade-amid-worries-over-trump-tariffs-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>阿里巴巴联合电子商务部门应对日益激烈的竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/alibaba-integrate-e-commerce-platforms-into-one-business-group-2024-11-21/</link><description>阿里巴巴集团周四在一份证券交易所文件中表示，该公司将首次将其国内和国际电子商务平台整合为一个由一位领导者运营的单一业务部门。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 10:14:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/alibaba-integrate-e-commerce-platforms-into-one-business-group-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>台湾称被监禁的前中国高官薄熙来之子正在探望</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-son-jailed-former-senior-chinese-official-bo-xilai-is-visiting-2024-11-21/</link><description>台湾政府周四表示，被监禁的中国前高级领导人薄熙来的儿子在与一名台湾公民结婚后，出于个人原因访问台湾，这对于与中国政治精英有联系的人来说是罕见的旅行。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 09:56:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-son-jailed-former-senior-chinese-official-bo-xilai-is-visiting-2024-11-21/</guid></item></channel></rss>